summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department and authorizing the sale and removal of alder timber, other hardwood forest materials, cottonwood, and certain salvageable logging residuals from City owned land in Townships 22 and 23 North, Range 7 East, W.M., and Townships 21, 22 and 23 North, Range 8 East, W.M., and Township 22 North, Range 9 East, W.M., in the Cedar River Watershed under contract with Masao Nakaso.
